The doge is in town

What is DogeTown?

DogeTown is a hyper-deflationary token build on the famous Binance Smart Chain. It has an total supply of 1bn tokens. The total supply will decrease because of burnings that the team will do ongoing the process. Our Doge will visit all cities in this beautiful world!

Mission, Vision and Goals

A project like DogeTown can gain a massive popularity in the crypto-meme coin space. Not just that! We are hyped for the upcoming NFTs of DogeTown, which will be a great producer for massive hype around this project. Through the good connected team, the project will be getting attention from a lot of famous influencer which have a lot of impact in the crypto space!

Tokenomics

Taxes for buys and sells are needed to build and develop the projects vision. The funds for realizing our visions we get from the taxes of buys and sells.

P3

  • Listing on different exchanges
  • Promotions spots on tracking platforms
  • Certik Audit
  • Articles from big magazines
  • Trending activities

Team & Safu

The CEO and Owner of DogeTown is doing KYC. Doing KYC is the most safe verification service you can do. While the KYC process, your data like ID-Card, Pictures and Videos of you will be saved by the KYC-platform. If there is any sign of scam or rug, the KYC-data will be forwarded to the government of that country and a police report is being created.

So being KYCed nowadays is the most safest thing which can happen to the investors, but also to the project.
